{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8bc0c73412","title":"对录荣臻关于中南军区部队二期整编工作报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cd6e251e36","index":0,"year":1952,"month":8,"day":24,"articleId":"8bc0c73412"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"242eb6b030","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8bc0c73412","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中国人民解放军代总参谋长衰荣臻1952年8月23日给毛泽东等的报告说，中南军区部队的二期整编方案，拟将第二十一兵团尚余的原陈明仁起义部队的1个师编为该兵团所属3个炮兵团。楚荣臻在报告中提出，“惟目前火炮装备条件不够，不可能按照将其三个炮兵团装备起来，势必再将其编掉，在政治上这是值得考虑的。因此，我们认为现二十一兵团尚有原起义的一个师，在这次整编中仍应作为一个师编留较为适宜”。"},{"id":"9ebf67f77c","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8bc0c73412","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈明仁，原国民党政府军将领，1949年8月与程潜率部在长沙起义。当时任中国人民解放军第二十一兵团司令员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e08b2b9bae","type":"title","text":"对慧荣臻关于中南军区部队二期整编工作报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8bc0c73412"},{"id":"242eb6b030","type":"paragraph","text":"陈明仁部应当留一个师，不应编掉，也不要编为炮兵团。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8bc0c73412"},{"id":"9ebf67f77c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8bc0c73412"},{"id":"89bddcbe52","type":"paragraph","text":"八月廿四日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8bc0c73412"}],"page":{"id":"4683fcbd54","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8bc0c73412","start":210,"end":210}}}},"__N_SSG":true}